    "body":  "Requested Change (UI only):\n\nAdd a short purpose tagline under the main Dashboard header:\n\nTrack, assess, and prove worker qualifications in regulated environments.\n\n\nAdd hover-tooltips on the top four dashboard tiles:\n\nQualified Workers: Workers who meet all assigned job requirements\n\nNeeds Review: Workers missing recent qualifications or nearing expiration\n\nNot Qualified: Workers missing critical skills or expired credentials\n\nActive Jobs: Roles with at least one worker assigned\n\nNo backend or data logic changes needed. Just UI-level updates.",
